0crisis%2C%20many%20lack%20the%20vocabulary%20to%20articulate%20it.%20And%20it%20is%20not%20their%20fault%2C%20says%20Jagadish%20Thaker%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Queensland%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20principal%20investigator%20of%20a%202023%20survey%20by%20the%20Yale%20Program%20on%20Climate%20Change%20Communication%20(YPCCC)%2C%20which%20indicated%20that%20more%20than%2090%20percent%20of%20Indians%20are%20concerned%20about%20global%20warming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opinion%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20lack%20of%20awareness%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20people%20are%20not%20worried%20about%20it%20%5Bclimate%20change%5D.%20It%20means%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20it%20is%20called%20global%20warming%20and%20that%20it%20is%20caused%20by%20human%20activities.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20bridging%20this%20ecological%20literacy%20chasm%20are%20youth%20like%20Soumya%2C%20who%20are%20venturing%20into%20the%20fringes%20of%20Odisha%20armed%20with%20cameras%20and%20ideas.%20Their%20content%20is%20rooted%20in%20native%20script%20to%20help%20India%E2%80%99s%20hinterland%20verbalise%20the%20realities%20unfolding%20in%20the%20fields%20and%20on%20their%20tables.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20creators%20are%20backed%20by%20Momentum%20Shifts%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20initiative%20building%20citizen-facing%20narratives%20for%20system%20changes%2C%20which%20believes%20in%20tailor-made%20content%20and%20humour%20being%20channelled%20into%20tackling%20ecological%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%2