oo%20much%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Use%20grafted%20saplings%20for%20faster%20results%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20Jamun%20from%20seed%20is%20possible%20but%20requires%20immense%20patience%2C%20as%20it%20can%20take%20eight%20to%2010%20years%20to%20fruit.%20Grafted%20saplings%2C%20however%2C%20are%20clones%20of%20mature%20trees%20and%20typically%20start%20bearing%20fruit%20in%20just%20four%20to%20five%20years.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20also%20have%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20fruit%20quality%20and%20tree%20size%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Water%20less%2C%20not%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamun%20is%20a%20hardy%2C%20drought-tolerant%20tree.%20During%20the%20monsoon%2C%20natural%20rainfall%20is%20usually%20sufficient.%20Only%20water%20if%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20dry%20spell%20or%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20growing%20it%20in%20a%20container.%20Let%20the%20topsoil%20dry%20slightly%20before%20watering%20again.%20Overwatering%2C%20especially%20in%20pots%2C%20can%20stunt%20growth%20or%20damage%20the%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Fruits%20stain%2C%20but%20soothe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Jamun%20stains%20your%20tongue%20and%20hands%20a%20deep%20purple%E2%80%94but%20it%E2%80%99s%20worth%20it.%20The%20fruit%20is%20low%20in%20calories%20but%20high%20in%20antioxidants%2C%20Vitamin%20C%2C%20and%20iron.%20It%20helps%20regulate%20blood%20sugar%20levels%2C%20aids%20digestion%2C%20improves%20immunity%2C%20and%20even%20benefits%20skin%20health.%20It%E2%80%99s%20your%20very%20own%20medicinal%20fruit%20basket!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Grow%20health%2C%20not%20just%20a%20tree%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlanting%20a%20Jamun%20tree%20is%20an%20act%20of%20slow%2C%20joyful%20patience.%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20give%20instant%20gratification%2C%20but%20in%20a%20few%20years%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20have%20a%20personal%20source%20of%20antioxidants%2C%20immunity%2C%20and%20nostalgia%20(wh