3ENot%20all%20persons%20on%20the%20roads%20are%20beggars%20%E2%80%93%20some%20may%20have%20lost%20their%20way.%20Some%20may%20have%20been%20driven%20out%20of%20their%20houses.%20Some%20are%20denied%20opportunities%20for%20being%20differently-abled.%20Some%20are%20mentally%20affected%20and%2C%20with%20no%20refuge%2C%20may%20have%20made%20the%20streets%20their%20home.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20harness%20the%20potential%20of%20every%20individual%20in%20this%20country.%20If%20all%20these%20people%20can%20be%20counselled%20and%20given%20an%20opportunity%2C%20then%20it%20can%20drive%20the%20nation%20towards%20prosperity.%20Let%20us%20support%20this%20Hero%20in%20what%20he%20is%20fighting%20to%20achieve!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1750819012000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-79-1750773063.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D455036%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Naveen%20Kumar%20left%20his%20comfortable%20engineering%20career%20to%20build%20a%20beggar-free%20India.%20Through%20his%20Atchayam%20Trust%2C%20he%20has%20helped%20over%201%2C400%20people%20living%20on%20the%20streets%20find%20jobs%2C%20shelter%2C%20and%20hope.%20His%20mission%20goes%20beyond%20charity%E2%80%94restoring%20dignity%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20a%20fresh%20start%20for%20every%20life%20he%20touches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shruthi%20Srinivasan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F455036%2Fbeggar-free-india-naveen-kumar-atchayam-trust%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2255%25%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Farms%20Wait%20for%20Rain%3A%20What%20a%20Late%20Monsoon%20Means%20in%202025%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20monsoon%20has%20arrived%20late%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20and%20for%20farmers%2C%20that